>mañana<\/strong> para empezar el día con claridad mental o en la <strong>noche<\/strong> para relajarte antes de dormir.<\/p>"}}},"block_order":["question_LyXwQE","question_hnFTYY","question_bV4jnW","question_WWY6aW"],"settings":{"text_font":"system_ui_n4","text_size":16,"text_line_height":"inherit","headline_font":"system_ui_n4","headline_size":20,"headline_line_height":"inherit","background_color":"linear-gradient(164deg, rgba(245, 245, 220, 1), rgba(247, 247, 247, 1) 18%)","question_color":"#2d4739","answer_color":"#000000","max_width":2000,"padding_top":25,"padding_bottom":2,"padding_left":10,"padding_right":10,"vertical_alignment":"center","image_location":"left","image_aspect_ratio":"4 \/ 3","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/DALL_E_2025-03-12_18.50.56_-_A_serene_and_modern_wellness-themed_image_featuring_a_wooden_spoon_filled_with_ashwagandha_powder_placed_on_a_natural_wooden_surface_with_soft_lighti.webp","media_radius":2,"media_shadow":true}},"sp_icon_list_NrcENB":{"type":"sp-icon-list","blocks":{"icon_FwEteF":{"type":"icon","settings":{"icon":"image","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/3.png","headline":"🌿 <strong>Equilibrio Natural<\/strong>","text":"La ashwagandha ayuda a reducir los niveles de cortisol, promoviendo un estado de calma y bienestar. Ideal para disminuir el estrés y mejorar la calidad del sueño.","link":""}},"icon_3PAkd6":{"type":"icon","settings":{"icon":"image","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/4.png","headline":"🧠 <strong>Consulta Psicológica GRATIS<\/strong>","text":"Con tu compra, recibirás una consulta psicológica gratuita para ayudarte a manejar el estrés y la ansiedad de manera efectiva.","link":""}},"icon_6U4Gex":{"type":"icon","settings":{"icon":"image","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/5.png","headline":"⚡ <strong>Energía y Enfoque<\/strong>","text":"Mejora tu resistencia al estrés y aumenta tu energía de forma natural, sin estimulantes ni efectos secundarios.","link":""}},"icon_9G4Mnq":{"type":"icon","settings":{"icon":"image","im